                            <et:Title>Samsung Magician fails to update itself securely</et:Title>
                            <et:Description>Samsung Magician is a management utility for Samsung SSDs. Prior to version 5.0, Samsung Magician checks for and retrieves updates over HTTP. Prior to version 5.1, Samsung Magician uses HTTPS to perform update operations, however it does not validate SSL certificates.</et:Description>
